In the inital implementation only limited operation were considered .
Below is the list of operations which will be tracked 
1)File open , read , write 
2)Connecting to black listed ip , reading and writing from that ip address(TCP)
3)Changing the mode or ownership of files 
4)Changing the uid of the process 

In the Intial implementation we will be considering only those system calls which 
will be returning 0 or non zero on success and -1 or -ve number on errors 

In the next release the following features are panned to be included 
1)tracking shared memory creation , attaching to shared memeory , readinga nd writing into teh shared memory
2)Tracking File copying 
3)tracking the child process  
4)Tracking UDP communication with the black listed ip address 
